49
00:02:23,620 --> 00:02:24,420
Who...?

50
00:02:26,020 --> 00:02:27,340
That night,

51
00:02:27,460 --> 00:02:28,820
someone saw

52
00:02:29,300 --> 00:02:31,220
a person fleeing
from the Southwest Pavilion.

53
00:02:31,220 --> 00:02:32,580
When he ran,

54
00:02:32,580 --> 00:02:34,220
he dropped the pendant he was carrying.

55
00:02:36,100 --> 00:02:37,300
The pendant

56
00:02:37,460 --> 00:02:39,580
is exactly the same
as what Bai Anyuan is wearing.

57
00:02:41,380 --> 00:02:42,580
It was the master of the Bai family,

58
00:02:43,740 --> 00:02:45,020
Bai Chengzhi.

59
00:02:50,980 --> 00:02:52,020
The Bai family...

60
00:02:55,700 --> 00:02:57,900
Your family

61
00:02:57,900 --> 00:02:59,660
has longstanding ties with ours.

62
00:02:59,780 --> 00:03:01,580
I do not wish

63
00:03:01,580 --> 00:03:04,540
to see you waste time

64
00:03:04,780 --> 00:03:06,620
on Buhan like this.

65
00:03:06,820 --> 00:03:09,260
Since you aren't on good terms,

66
00:03:09,420 --> 00:03:11,300
why not divorce

67
00:03:12,540 --> 00:03:14,060
and part ways?

68
00:03:15,660 --> 00:03:16,460
Grandmother,

69
00:03:16,900 --> 00:03:18,780
did I do something wrong?

70
00:03:21,260 --> 00:03:25,580
It's the Ye family
that is not worthy of the Bai family.

71
00:03:30,700 --> 00:03:31,700
Ms. Bai.

72
00:03:32,580 --> 00:03:33,580
Please get up.

73
00:03:39,780 --> 00:03:41,780
Have you had a physician check on you?

74
00:03:41,940 --> 00:03:42,940
Madam,

75
00:03:43,220 --> 00:03:45,500
Ms. Bai hasn't had her period
for two months.

76
00:03:45,740 --> 00:03:48,060
We had the renowned gynecologist
from Huichun Hall

77
00:03:48,060 --> 00:03:48,860
examine her yesterday.

78
00:03:48,860 --> 00:03:49,460
The physician said

79
00:03:49,460 --> 00:03:51,060
Ms. Bai is two months pregnant...

80
00:03:51,060 --> 00:03:51,980
Jinling.

81
00:03:55,300 --> 00:03:56,180
Grandmother,

82
00:03:56,180 --> 00:03:58,220
it's just been a couple of months.

83
00:03:58,220 --> 00:03:59,220
The fetus is unstable.

84
00:03:59,580 --> 00:04:02,420
I was going to let you know

85
00:04:02,660 --> 00:04:04,020
the good news

86
00:04:05,260 --> 00:04:06,420
when it's stable.

87
00:04:11,780 --> 00:04:14,020
Buhan didn't want to touch me
even when drunk.

88
00:04:14,620 --> 00:04:16,620
Am I really not as good as that wretch?

89
00:04:20,300 --> 00:04:21,620
From now on,

90
00:04:22,540 --> 00:04:24,740
you're carrying Ye Buhan's child.

91
00:04:39,940 --> 00:04:42,620
Since Ms. Bai is two months pregnant,

92
00:04:42,820 --> 00:04:45,220
