to give birth to the child

93
00:04:45,220 --> 00:04:47,780
and we'll raise them with great care.

94
00:04:47,780 --> 00:04:48,580
Grandmother,

95
00:04:48,940 --> 00:04:50,020
you promised me

96
00:04:50,020 --> 00:04:51,420
we would face the Bai family together.

97
00:04:52,100 --> 00:04:53,780
Are you going to give up

98
00:04:53,780 --> 00:04:55,060
because Bai Anyuan is pregnant?

99
00:04:55,060 --> 00:04:56,420
This is not giving up.

100
00:04:56,820 --> 00:05:00,100
The Qixiang Pavilion needs
the Bai family's money.

101
00:05:00,420 --> 00:05:01,220
Besides,

102
00:05:01,940 --> 00:05:05,060
