103
00:05:05,420 --> 00:05:07,500
But I've never had any feelings for her.

104
00:05:07,980 --> 00:05:09,020
Her child

105
00:05:09,020 --> 00:05:10,380
may not even be a Ye.

106
00:05:10,380 --> 00:05:11,980
Neither are you.

107
00:05:13,380 --> 00:05:14,140
Grandmother,

108
00:05:15,060 --> 00:05:16,060
