111
00:05:22,780 --> 00:05:24,620
You are not Cheng's son.

112
00:05:24,620 --> 00:05:26,180
So you've been deceiving me.

113
00:05:26,620 --> 00:05:28,620
You told me I was the only child
of the Ye family.

114
00:05:29,980 --> 00:05:31,980
No wonder you turned so emotional

115
00:05:31,980 --> 00:05:33,020
