117
00:05:36,180 --> 00:05:36,860
Fine.

118
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:38,420
I'll leave.

119
00:05:39,700 --> 00:05:40,420
Buhan!

120
00:05:40,420 --> 00:05:41,380
Meng.

121
00:05:45,260 --> 00:05:45,940
This one.

122
00:05:46,020 --> 00:05:46,660
Okay.

